# Airbnb Clone - User Stories

This document translates the use case diagram interactions into user stories for the Airbnb Clone project.

---

## 1. User Registration
**As a user**, I want to register an account so that I can access the platform and manage my bookings or listings.

---

## 2. Property Listing
**As a host**, I want to list my property with details like photos, price, and availability so that potential guests can find and book it.

---

## 3. Property Booking
**As a guest**, I want to search for available properties and make a booking so that I can stay at my chosen location.

---

## 4. Payment Processing
**As a user**, I want to securely pay for a booking or receive payments for my listed property so that transactions are handled safely and efficiently.

---

## 5. Reviews and Ratings
**As a guest or host**, I want to leave and view reviews for properties and users so that I can make informed decisions and build trust in the community.

